title: Regulator V1 ICE TEC1 SemiTec I with SPG - EN250A

photos.alt: Automat V1 ICE TEC1 SemiTec I z manometrem - EN250A

description:
Product description

V1 ICE TEC1 SemiTec I - equivalent of V2 designed for divers using a single tank.

The regulator is prepared for diving under ice (cold waters) and allows for ideal arrangement of hoses both in configuration with an octopus as well as with a long hose and backup on a bungee.

 

V1 ICE TEC1 SemiTec I Semi Tec includes:

- 1 x first stage V1 ICE, diaphragm with Cold Kit, 4 x LP, 2 x HP

- 2 x second stage TEC2, balanced with Venturi regulation and breathing resistance regulation

- 1 x hose LP 61 cm

- 1 x hose LP 193 cm

- 1 x hose HP 61 cm

- 1 x manometer Tecline 300 bar

- 2 x piston carabiner

- 1 x bungee for hanging the second stage (in 2 versions as in the DIR version for double set)

- 1 x Tecline regulator's bag
